There,are,a,lot,of,apps,available,online,and,it,can,be,difficult,to,sort,through,them,to,identify,which,ones,are,safest,to,use,The,WeatherRepo,is,a,service,designed,to,determine,the,security,of,a,given,application,and,quantify,information,about,app,safety,in,a,way,that,both,developers,and,users,can,understand,The,WeatherRepo,s,app,safety,information,can,be,retrieved,programmatically,via,REST,calls